347
00:18:00.695 --> 00:18:01.795
Mr. Mouri.

348
00:18:11.495 --> 00:18:14.495
What happened, Mr. Mouri?

349
00:18:14.495 --> 00:18:16.795
I happened to punish the drunkard a bit,

350
00:18:16.795 --> 00:18:18.395
and this is the outcome.

351
00:18:18.395 --> 00:18:20.295
Don't worry about it at all.

352
00:18:20.295 --> 00:18:21.995
A bit, huh?

353
00:18:23.195 --> 00:18:24.895
Well, I guess it serves him right.

354
00:18:24.895 --> 00:18:28.695
Oh, by the way, where's Kurumazaki?

355
00:18:28.695 --> 00:18:32.695
He was being asked to do something by Pops Kogoro a while ago.

356
00:18:34.295 --> 00:18:38.795
Mr. Mouri, what did you ask Kurumazaki to do?

357
00:18:38.795 --> 00:18:41.095
More than that, Inspector Ayanokoji,

358
00:18:41.095 --> 00:18:42.895
did you check on it?

359
00:18:42.895 --> 00:18:44.895
The packages of Ogura flavored boxes

360
00:18:44.895 --> 00:18:46.495
that were line out in the shop.

361
00:18:46.495 --> 00:18:47.595
Yes.

362
00:18:47.595 --> 00:18:52.095
Rice oil was found around the ogura flavor seals.

363
00:18:52.095 --> 00:18:53.395
Rice oil?

364
00:18:53.395 --> 00:18:57.795
We use rice oil as a parting agent at our shop.

365
00:18:59.795 --> 00:19:03.095
Hey, what's a parting agent?

366
00:19:03.095 --> 00:19:04.495
It's oil that is brushed onto the mold

367
00:19:04.495 --> 00:19:06.895
before that batter is poured into the mold

368
00:19:06.895 --> 00:19:08.895
so that it comes off easily after it's cooked.

369
00:19:08.895 --> 00:19:13.795
But why would that be on the ogura seals?

370
00:19:13.795 --> 00:19:15.995
It wasn't on the seals.

371
00:19:15.995 --> 00:19:18.295
It was put on, deliberately.

372
00:19:18.295 --> 00:19:20.995
Before the ogura seals were pasted on.

373
00:19:20.995 --> 00:19:22.795
40 boxes of Ogura flavor,

374
00:19:22.795 --> 00:19:24.295
40 boxes of Maccha flavor

375
00:19:24.295 --> 00:19:26.395
