383
00:19:47.695 --> 00:19:50.695
Then, a new ogura seal is pasted on.

384
00:19:50.695 --> 00:19:52.595
Two people work on the 10 boxes.

385
00:19:52.595 --> 00:19:55.195
The first boxes of ogura that are lined out

386
00:19:55.195 --> 00:19:57.095
