405
00:20:50.695 --> 00:20:52.195
You do something like this just for that reason?

406
00:20:52.195 --> 00:20:54.695
It's not just for a reason like that!

407
00:20:54.695 --> 00:20:57.195
It's nothing like that.

408
00:20:57.195 --> 00:21:00.095
That's the very reason why we didn't want to sell

409
00:21:00.095 --> 00:21:03.495
